Tottenham have been offered free agent striker Jonas. 

The 30-year-old Brazilian has interest from Benfica and has also been pushed to Sunderland.

Jonas has been released by Valencia and is keen on a move to the Premier League but knows he could be a regular starter at Benfica. 

